<h3 id="pl-2-3-control-enhancement-m-h">PL-2 (3) Control Enhancement (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization plans and coordinates security-related activities affecting the information system with [Assignment: organization-defined individuals or groups] before conducting such activities in order to reduce the impact on other organizational entities.</p>

